Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂～喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂～喂～
